snippet.textDisplay: Dude. I love your channel, despite trying my hardest for ten years to hate you... I tried so, so hard to hate you, because you addicted my daughter to Minecraft, and that's what I heard about 24/7--Minecraft and PewDiePie. And then, she got me addicted to Minecraft. And then I became addicted to PewDiePie. And I fell in love. And then.......this. Your 30-day break after your big lead-up into taking a break from YouTube, with an unforeseen length of absence being your big bell ringer. We thought it would be 6 months to a year. I thought, "Good. I can finally get a break from this love/hate relationship I've been suffering through for a decade. Finally, some reprieve". But no, you're back. Thirty days later. I want to hate you for this publicity stunt, but it was brilliant. So I still love and hate you. The End.
